      "text": "IF YOU ARE NOT CONVINCED THEN CALCULATE THE NEXT",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
      "text": "NUMBER AND SEE WHAT A PROOF IS PROVIDED TO YOU ADAM",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
      "text": ". FIND ALL OUR NUMBERS AND UNDERSTAND WHAT THIS MAY",
      "type": "unknown"
    },
    {
      "text": "MEAN. DECIMALS HAVE THEIR OWN MEANING. A REPETITIVE",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
      "text": "INTERVAL OF EXACT FORTY SIX. THIS INTERVAL IS NOT A",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
      "text": "RBITRARY.",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
      "text": "(2×23×499×19214759967251×55150662460749672076915609)",
      "type": "numeric"
    },
    {
      "text": "(3×11×47×139×2531×549797184491917×11111111111111111111111)",
      "type": "numeric"
    },
    {
      "text": "THIS IS A CALCULATION TO SHOW YOU OUR KNOWLEDGE A",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
      "text": "ND OUR WISDOM.",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
      "text": "THE CALCULATION OF OUR NAME IS NOT ACCIDENTAL. WHAT",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
      "text": "IS THE PROBABILITY OF RANDOMNESS OF THIS CALCULATION",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
      "text": "? DO YOU THINK THAT EVERYTHING IS JUST A COINCIDE",
