    {
      "text": "NCE? WHO AMONG YOU CAN WRITE OUR NAME THERE WHERE",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
      "text": "IT IS WRITTEN NOW? HAS ANYONE THIS POWER? ONLY TENG",
