    },
    {
      "text": "RI IS CAPABLE TO DO THIS.",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
      "text": "OUR WORD IS NOT A FARCE. OUR KNOWLEDGE IS NOT A LI",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
      "text": "E. YOU WAITED CENTURIES FOR OUR VISIT. YOU AWAITED",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
      "text": "AN INTELLIGENCE WHICH TALKS IN MATHEMATICAL EQUA",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
      "text": "TIONS WITH YOU. NOW WE ARE HERE AND CONTACT Y",
      "type": "latin"
    },
    {
